---
title: Sticky Haloumi, Chicken & Root Veggie Medley with Almonds & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Sweet honey comes together in a glaze for squeaky haloumi that really takes it the next level. Add a touch of fragrance with
thyme and a herby mayo to make your mouth water. Along with a medley of colourful veggies, this is the one to watch.
